The raw plot data were analysed in linear mixed model in PROC Mixed of SAS using REML. In WS conditions, the two field experiments per population were pooled using a combined analysis. The adjusted means for each line were estimated using the following linear model:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
